body:
[Here's another link if the first one doesn't work](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tzSRw5JJ45s)

My very first Pentakill on League of Legends, and it's with SINGED of all characters! WHOEVER SAYS SUCH A FEAT IS IMPOSSIBLE, READ IT AND WEEP!

Anywho, the video belongs to Chook Chook, a good friend of mine: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCy7V...

And the idea to use clips and references to Jojo's Bizarre Adventure, I have to say the idea was originally from Munchyjr so go watch his vids as he inspired me in my editing: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCSLTvMEi7uoHPl349o_GVXg

And I do not own anything in this video. I don't own Jojo's Bizarre Adventure, or League of Legends as they both belong to their own respectful owners
